ost so nice had to reblog it twice and force it down everyone&rsquo;s throats</p></blockquote><p><i>post so nice had to</i></p><p><i>reblog it twice and force it</i></p><p><i>down everyone’s throats</i></p><p><small>Beep boop! I look for accidental haiku posts. Sometimes I mess up.</small></p></blockquote>","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"elierlick","active":true,"theme":{"header_full_width":3000,"header_full_height":1055,"avatar_shape":"square","background_color":"#F6F6F6","body_font":"Helvetica Neue","header_bounds":"","header_image":"https://64.media.tumblr.com/ceb0aa9501fb5df65b643121e98aa573/e25990b1c8737908-39/s3000x1055/b4cabf749504283d7da25069ca88d0b4c074b2a5.png","header_image_focused":"https://64.media.tumblr.com/ceb0aa9501fb5df65b643121e98aa573/e25990b1c8737908-39/s2048x3072/4561fb2ab57595d802bb8a4ff7ff98cdf7945f23.png","header_image_poster":"","header_image_scaled":"https://64.media.tumblr.com/ceb0aa9501fb5df65b643121e98aa573/e25990b1c8737908-39/s2048x3072/4561fb2ab57595d802bb8a4ff7ff98cdf7945f23.png","header_stretch":true,"link_color":"#81B4D2","show_avatar":true,"show_description":true,"show_header_image":true,"show_title":true,"title_color":"#444444","title_font":"Helvetica Neue","title_font_weight":"bold"},"share_likes":false,"share_following":false,"can_be_followed":true},"post":{"id":"810115165023502336"},"content_raw":"<p><figure class=\"tmblr-full\" data-orig-height=\"1280\" data-orig-width=\"720\" data-npf='{\"type\":\"video\",\"provider\":\"tumblr\",\"url\":\"https://va.media.tumblr.com/tumblr_tbcd3yMfOD1rig9z5.mp4\",\"media\":{\"url\":\"https://va.media.tumblr.com/tumblr_tbcd3yMfOD1rig9z5.mp4\",\"type\":\"video/mp4\",\"width\":720,\"height\":1280},\"poster\":[{\"media_key\":\"46ec75ba4ba2fa820c6c9a7f9ba5de94:bb706b724ce49b35-4d\",\"type\":\"image/jpeg\",\"width\":456,\"height\":810,\"url\":\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/46ec75ba4ba2fa820c6c9a7f9ba5de94/bb706b724ce49b35-4d/s540x810/a52a627d3e61cd769f6a62721c3fcae575fa69f3.jpg\"}]}'><video controls=\"c